The paper deals with the Directed Feedback Vertex Set problem, which is a graph covering problem. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) or Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) categories. The paper also mentions a general methodology for iterative-compression based algorithms, which is a technique used in computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph theory (cs.CC). Finally, the paper discusses the Multicut and Directed Subset Feedback Vertex Set problems, which are related to graph theory and optimization (cs.GT). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.CG, cs.CC, and cs.GT, in that order.
